Summary[edit]

Asturianu: Bandera d'Asturies.
Deutsch: Flagge von Asturien.
Español: Bandera de Asturias.
English: Flag of the Asturias.
Русский: Флаг Астурии.

Ley 4/90, de 19 de diciembre, de la Bandera del Principado de Asturias

Source[edit]

Reedited version of Banderas first uploaded as Image:Bandera asturias.svg with some fixing by Huhsunqu. It Repleces first version uploaded by kooma from Open Clip Art Library.
